<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0defe6f0-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s4515"><num value="4515">§ 4515.</num><heading> Appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are appropriated to the James Madison Memorial Trust Fund $20,000,000 to carry out the provisions of this chapter, $10,000,000 of which shall be available on <date date="1987-11-01">November 1, 1987</date>, and to remain available until expended; and $10,000,000 of which shall be available on <date date="1988-11-01">November 1, 1988</date>, and to remain available until expended.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0defe6f1-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/500/s101/b/tVIII/s816">Pub. L. 99–500, § 101(b) [title VIII, § 816]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-18">Oct. 18, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/1783-39">100 Stat. 1783–39</ref>, 1783–81, and <ref href="/us/pl/99/591/s101/b/tVIII/s816">Pub. L. 99–591, § 101(b) [title VIII, § 816]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-30">Oct. 30, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3341-39">100 Stat. 3341–39</ref>, 3341–81.)</sourceCredit>
